descript.abstract: Outline representing the area of hydrography features. Hydrography features are idenified as subtypes. Stream - outline of a hydrography feature less than 20' across on the ground. River - outline of a hydrography feature greater than 20' across on the ground. Lakes and Detention Ponds, and Ponds - outline of an enclosed hydrography feature.
descript.purpose: The purpose of this data set is to show the outline representing the area of hydrography features. Hydrography features are idenified as subtypes. Stream - outline of a hydrography feature less than 20' across on the ground. River - outline of a hydrography feature greater than 20' across on the ground. Lakes and Detention Ponds, and Ponds - outline of an enclosed hydrography feature.
